title: Sublime Rules (feat. Justin Silver)
description: Jacob shaved his head and refused let the rest of the crew see how he looked. Jay & Dan discuss which exotic animals they would eat if they had too. The gang talks about the hottest kids from their high schools and later, Christine and Justin Silver argue about just how good the band Sublime was.
